import React from 'react'
import ProductCard from '../components/ProductCard'
import FooterSection from '../sections/FooterSection'

import ProductGridSection from '../sections/ProductGridSection'

  return (
    <>
      <MainMenuSection />
      <ProductGridSection />
      <FooterSection />
    </>

}

export default HomeView
